description: I always save the toughest scene ideas for esteemed visitors like Wenona. Scene 1 and 2 are back to back suspensions with no break! Being a masochist, she hates tickling, so I did lots of that. Scene 3 is a spin off of the "wax on, wax off" routine. And in the 4th scene in the fish tank,she finds out for the first time just how wicked a roll of harmless looking electrical tape can be. Kudos to one of the best in the industry, Wenona.
title: Wenona
